Importing the Data (Connect to Data Source) 9


Raw File Link - https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/shilongzhuang/pizza-sales



This dataset has a single table with few columns of data


1. Save the file on your device.

2. Open Tableau Desktop.

3. On the Tableau Connect Pane Click Microsoft Excel.

4. Brows e to the location of the excel file downloaded and click Open

5. Preview of the data will be displayed.

6. Click on Sheet 1.
